    27â†’### In libraries
    28â†’
    29â†’Libraries should link only to the `log` crate, and use the provided macros to
    30â†’log whatever information will be useful to downstream consumers:
    58â†’### In executables
    59â†’
    60â†’In order to produce log output, executables have to use a logger implementation compatible with the facade.
    61â†’There are many available implementations to choose from, here are some options:
